+        # Setting only the list (old code) left DeltaNet capturing nothing -> the
+        # bare-tensor return tripped ``hidden, aux = hidden`` ("too many values to
+        # unpack"); routing through ``set_dflash_layers_to_capture`` (also old)
+        # AttributeError'd on the dense backbone. Set the list AND mark the flags
+        # so EAGLE3 works on whichever backbone is loaded (each forward reads one;
